  "title": "Data Analyst [EAST LOCATION]",
  "description": "<h2>Job Description</h2><ul><li><p>Collect, analyse, and visualise data to produce monthly operational and performance reports.</p></li><li><p>Identify trends and patterns to provide actionable insights and recommendations.</p></li><li><p>Maintain and manage databases to ensure data accuracy, consistency, and integrity.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and deliver presentations during monthly review meetings with management and clients.</p></li><li><p>Proactively liaise with clients to understand reporting requirements and address data-related queries.</p></li></ul><h2>Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Relevant working experience in data analysis, reporting, or a related field is preferred; <strong>fresh graduates are welcome to apply</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Able to work at <strong>East location(s)</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>5-day work week</strong>; candidates should be prepared to work <strong>flexible or shift hours</strong> when required.</p></li><li><p>Background or exposure to <strong>robotics, automation, or related technologies</strong> is an advantage.</p></li><li><p>Good analytical, communication, and presentation skills.</p></li></ul><h2>Remuneration</h2><ul><li><p><strong>Salary Range:</strong> SGD <strong>4,500 – 5,300</strong>, commensurate with experience and qualifications.</p></li></ul>",
